oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Walker family home near the Clinch River
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The Walker family home near the Clinch River, Walker's Ford. Shows people on lawn and in windows.
It was torn down when Norris Lake was formed in 1935.
